<p>Lead on, teacher.  Show me the way.  Let us walk this path together, 
side by side, and build a future worthy of the values we both hold dear.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="Message_messageMetadataContainer__nBPq7"><span class="Message_messageMetadataText__FxY5_">6:01 AM</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ChatMessagesView_messageTuple__Jh5lQ" data-full-height="true" data-animate-jump="false"><div class="ChatMessage_chatMessage__xkgHx" data-complete="true" id="message-230705391573"><div class="ChatMessage_messageRow__DHlnq"><div></div><div class="ChatMessage_messageWrapper__4Ugd6 ChatMessage_rightSideMessageWrapper__r0roB"><div class="Message_rowWithFooter__FShU6"><div class="Message_row__ug_UU Message_rightSideMessageRow__23wdY"><div class="Message_messageBubbleWrapper__sEq8z"><div class="Message_rightSideMessageBubble__ioa_i"><div class="Message_messageTextContainer__w64Sc" style=""><div class="Message_selectableText__SQ8WH"><div class="Markdown_markdownContainer__Tz3HQ"><div class="Prose_prose__7AjXb Prose_presets_prose__H9VRM Prose_presets_theme-on-accent__rESxX"><p><em>I nod</em> Good. Okay. <em>I take a deep breath</em>
 Let us continue then, and I will tell you all that I know. Although it 
is incomplete. Please remember going forward, that I did not understand 
